---
import '../styles/tokens.css';
---

<section class="services wrap" id="servicios" data-reveal>
  <span class="sec-eyebrow">// servicios</span>
  <h2 class="sec-title">Lo que construimos</h2>
  <p class="sec-desc">Cinco formas de quitarte trabajo manual de encima, con el mismo equipo de principio a fin.</p>

  <div class="services-grid">

    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Páginas web</h3>
      <p>Diseño y desarrollo a medida, rápidas, pensadas para convertir.</p>
      <div class="service-stack"><span>Figma</span><span>Framer</span><span>Next.js</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2"/><line x1="11" y1="18" x2="13" y2="18"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Apps</h3>
      <p>Aplicaciones móviles nativas para iOS y Android, de la idea a las stores.</p>
      <div class="service-stack"><span>Flutter</span><span>Swift</span><span>Firebase</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 3"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>SaaS</h3>
      <p>Plataformas web con suscripción, paneles de gestión y pagos integrados.</p>
      <div class="service-stack"><span>Supabase</span><span>Stripe</span><span>Vercel</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2l2.5 5.5L20 9l-5.5 2.5L12 17l-2.5-5.5L4 9l5.5-1.5L12 2z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Automatización con IA</h3>
      <p>Procesos manuales convertidos en flujos automáticos.</p>
      <div class="service-stack"><span>Claude</span><span>n8n</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 1 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 1 1-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 1 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 1 1 0-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 1 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 1 1 4 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 1 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 1 1 0 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Mantenimiento</h3>
      <p>Actualizaciones, seguridad, soporte continuo sin sustos.</p>
      <div class="service-stack"><span>VS Code</span><span>Next.js</span><span>Sentry</span></div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    padding-top: 70px;
    padding-bottom: 70px;
  }
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .service-card {
    background: var(--bg-raised);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 22px;
  }
  .service-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 9px;
    background: var(--amber-dim);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    color: var(--amber);
  }
  .service-icon svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
  }
  .service-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .service-card p {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .service-stack {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .service-stack span {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--line);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }

  [data-reveal] {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(8px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  [data-reveal].is-revealed {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
